Comment = Site visit becaue spotty xmit. Not sure if it's a power issue or a signal strength issue. Checked all wiring, changed battery from 100 amp/hour to 55 amp/hr, did a power-up reset. DCP light did not blink during xmits. Removed DA H522 #1934 Rev S. Installed DA H522 #1549 Rev P, firmware 4.45. Random was received. 1545 GMT self-timed was missed, so stayed around for another one. Also missed that one- light in DCP did not come on, but did when forced a self-timed. Set DCP to send randoms if value >1.0 so should be all the time. Offset as found and as left = 21.120 in Level-A.
